Title: Krishkare Argan Oil Hair Protection Kit(Set of 5)
Description: About Argan OilFound exclusively in Morocco, this oil is also called Liquid Gold because it makes hair healthy, shiny and thick. It packs a powerful punch of nutrition, hair repair and hair fall control, giving you the shiny, thick and healthy hair of your dreams.1. Hair Serum: Formulated to invigorate the scalp and promote hair growth while reducing and preventing hair fall. Leave in. When using as styling agent, put two or three drops into your palm, and spread through your tresses.4.
